个工作日\\n- 今天是周五，距离季度末还有4个工作日\\n\\n**季度汇总任务将在2026年3月31日（周二）执行。**\\n</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774602071323\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:215b7619-c198-4ed9-89bf-88e6c89cfee6\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本月的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本月最…\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本月的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本月最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本月最…\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774602052187,\n      \"sessionId\": \"140b1645-64a5-4cd9-9644-a5ce16176cdf\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44166,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/140b1645-64a5-4cd9-9644-a5ce16176cdf.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the calendar to determine if today (March 27, 2026, Friday) is the last working day of March 2026.\\n\\nMarch 2026:\\n- March 1 (Sun)\\n- March 2 (Mon) - working day\\n- March 3 (Tue) - working day\\n- March 4 (Wed) - working day\\n- March 5 (Thu) - working day\\n- March 6 (Fri) - working day\\n- March 7 (Sat)\\n- March 8 (Sun)\\n- March 9 (Mon) - working day\\n- March 10 (Tue) - working day\\n- March 11 (Wed) - working day\\n- March 12 (Thu) - working day\\n\\n\\n- March 13 (Fri) - working day\\n- March 14 (Sat)\\n- March 15 (Sun)\\n- March 16 (Mon) - working day\\n- March 17 (Tue) - working day\\n- March 18 (Wed) - working day\\n- March 19 (Thu) - working day\\n- March 20 (Fri) - working day\\n- March 21 (Sat)\\n- March 22 (Sun)\\n- March 23 (Mon) - working day\\n- March 24 